### Backend

#### [MODIFY] [authController.js](file:///m:/Vibe%20Coding/MediAi/server/controllers/authController.js)
- Add new `googleLogin` controller function
- Receives `{ credential }` (Google ID token) from frontend
- Verifies token via Google's `https://oauth2.googleapis.com/tokeninfo` endpoint (no npm package needed)
- Extracts `email`, `name`, `picture` from verified token
- Searches Patient → Doctor → Admin collections for matching email
- If found → login to existing account (same profile!)
- If not found → check if email is in `ADMIN_EMAILS` → create Admin or Patient accordingly
- Doctors are never auto-created via Google (they need specialization etc.) — only existing doctor accounts can login via Google
- Returns JWT token + user data (identical format to manual login)

